---
const companyName = "Markae Closets and Design";
const websiteUrl = "https://markaeclosets.com";
const email = "sales@markaeclosets.com";
const lastUpdated = new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-CA');
---

<div class="bg-white py-8 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        This Privacy Policy explains how {companyName} ("we," "us," or "our"), with our head office in Ontario, Canada, collects, uses, and protects your personal information when you use our website {websiteUrl} (the "Site").
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We collect the following types of information:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
        <li>Analytics Data: We use Google Analytics to collect anonymous information about how visitors use our Site.</li>
        <li>Contact Form Data: When you submit our contact form, we collect your name, email address, and message content.</li>
        <li>Email Subscription: Your email address is added to our company mailing list when you fill out forms on our website.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
        <li>Analytics Data: We use this information to improve our Site and understand user behavior.</li>
        <li>Contact Form Data: We use this information to respond to your inquiries and provide customer service.</li>
        <li>Email Marketing: We use your email address to send you marketing communications about our kitchen cabinetry products and services.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Consent</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        By filling out forms on our website, you consent to the collection and use of your information as described in this policy. For email marketing, you can unsubscribe at any time using the link provided in each email.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Data Protection and Storage</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        We implement reasonable security measures to protect your personal information. Please note that your data may be stored on servers located outside of Canada. By using our Site, you consent to this potential cross-border data transfer.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">6. Data Retention</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        We retain your personal information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy or as required by law.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Under Ontario and Canadian privacy laws, you have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. To exercise these rights, please contact us using the information provided in Section 11.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">8. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        We use Google Analytics, which may collect and process data according to its own policies. Please review Google's privacy policy for more information.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">9. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Our Site is not intended for children under 13 years of age, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">11. Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
      <address class="not-italic">
        <p>{companyName}</p>
        <p>{email}</p>
      </address>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>